      ],
      "source": "https://www.uniquehistoryofpensacola.com/post/santa-rosa-s-dickerson-city-1918"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The original hotel was a two‑story wood‑frame building that served travelers between Milton and Pensacola.",
